Instead of using `updateItemAt` try to use `notifyItemMoved(fromPosition, toPosition)` which is method provided by `RecyclerView.Adapter`. 

    override fun onItemMove(fromPosition: Int, toPosition: Int) {
        notifyItemMoved(fromPosition, toPosition)
    }

